    "bio": "Founder @RoboMarketing \n\nI help businesses automate communication with chatbots and AI. Focused on WhatsApp, Messenger, Instagram, and website automation. \n\nWriting about practical automation strategies, AI tools, and conversational design. \n\nPassionate about building smart systems that save time and increase efficiency.",
